DESCRIPTION<br>
Lafayette Barton is a brand-new renovation in a historic preservation building in downtown Buffalo. In one of the most up and coming neighborhoods in the area, Lafayette Barton Apartments boast all new flooring, appliances, drywall, carpeting, and other amenities. Each unit is equipped with washer/dryer hookups for your convenience. These wonderful apartments sit on Lafayette between Barton St and Herkimer St., just minutes away from the Elmwood Village! The perfect for location anyone looking for affordable housing in an exciting area of Buffalo!<br>
